{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821450/extras/logoabouthtegame.png?t=1727881905\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821450/extras/5th_clip_GIFsandsofhope.gif.gif?t=1727881905\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A little game about exploring a desert and restoring its water flow...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Among other things!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821450/extras/4th_clip_GIFsandsofhope.gif?t=1727881905\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821450/extras/3rd_clip_GIFsandsofhope.gif.gif?t=1727881905\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Run, build and Hover across the sandy landscapes of the desert to uncover the secrets of Cydonia's Village. Find the mysterious ancestors' shrines to collect flow crystals and return the water flow of the desert. Meet other villagers and give them a hand in their activites along the way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821450/extras/2nd_clip_GIFsandsofhope.gif?t=1727881905\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821450/extras/7th_clip_GIFsandsofhope.gif.gif?t=1727881905\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821450/extras/1st_clip_GIFsandsofhope.gif?t=1727881905\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><im